T1  - Priority Update Intervals and Anomalies in Dynamic Ratio Type Job Shop Scheduling Rules
AU  - Adam, Nabil R.
AU  - Surkis, Julius
Y1  - 1980/12/01
PY  - 1980
DA  - 1980/12/01
