PB  - INFORMS
N2  - In this note we investigate extremal optimization over Leontief substitution systems. Such problems arise naturally in discounted Markov decision problems and in problems involving the control of economic systems. We develop both bounds on the objective value of a Leontief substitution system subject to perturbations and an algorithm for finding and improving perturbations.
